      responses:
        '200':
          description: Create Knowledge Graph
      tags:
        - Knowledge Graph
      description: >-
        ## 1️⃣ Overview


        **Purpose:**  

        Creates a knowledge graph from a specific file within a workspace.


        ---


        ## 2️⃣ Endpoint


        ``` bash

        POST
        /ai/api/v2/knowledge-graph/create?file_id={file_id}&workspace_id={workspace_id}

         ```

        ---


        ## 3️⃣ Query Parameters


        | Parameter | Type | Required | Description |

        | --- | --- | --- | --- |

        | file_id | string | ✅ Yes | The ID of the file to create the knowledge
        graph from |

        | workspace_id | string | ✅ Yes | Workspace identifier where the
        knowledge graph will be created |


        ---


        ## 4️⃣ Authentication


        Requires authentication using:


        ``` bash

        x-auth-token: <token>

         ```

        ---


        ## 5️⃣ Request Headers


        | Header | Required |

        | --- | --- |

        | x-auth-token | ✅ Yes |


        ---


        ## 6️⃣ Example Request


        ``` bash

        curl -X POST
        "https://kg.datagol.ai/ai/api/v2/knowledge-graph/create?file_id={file_id}&workspace_id={workspace_id}"
        \

        -H "x-auth-token: <token>"

         ```

        ---


